commit.message:
Add series for each BAC color
Add undo functionality for each series

Put timer-scheduled updates into module
Add graph capability to handle undo add drink
Put menu into toolbar

Change to update every minute
Viewport maximum is 1 hr
Graph set to scrollable

Add comments for future changes
Change from line graph to scatter plot
Change update to every 30 seconds

Add comments for future changes
Change from line graph to scatter plot

Change notification to pop up on drink, not start (reset modified to account)
Change icon as well as notification icon

Change clicking notification to redirect to existing activity (instead of restarting)
Added "exit" feature to close notification and application

Previous commit may not have worked - change to adding service to foreground
Notification now displaying (still have to change intent on click)
Add ContinueService class which extends service - set up to keep app running in background

Updates every 10s now
Y_max is now set to 1.25 highest point on graph, not current point
Changed some graph parameters (bounds, gridColor, series color update)

Changed reset function to simply restart the activity
Graph setup/display was moved after BACDisplay so updated BAC would be displayed
dateToTimeDouble was removed as it was inconsistent when transitioning to the next min or hour
graph is now displayed based on second of day + day of year -> formatted the same way
Need to determine if year transition is significant enough to account for
X and Y axis bounds are now automatically set based on given data
Graph is invisible onCreate and set to visible in setup
Replaced update function with automatic minute updates

Changed from Java Date/Calendar to Joda Time (DateTime)
Added graph visualization
Settings submit now restarts the activity

Changed initial and 0 drink color (blue)
Restructured code

Changed background color for front page
Removed redundant outer relative layout in content_demo and made time texts white
Added white to colors

Made snackbar color same as BAC_color()
Changed color for BAC display again

Changed colors in xml files and upped the minimum SDK API to 21
Implemented save and load for settings
Changed color settings
Redid BAC formula
Reverted sexSelected method (onClick)
Updated changing color to toolbar and floating action button
Added color feature that changes with BAC increase

Fixed bug in update by updating calendar on call
Reset now clears time text

Changed update and snackbar undo timeDisplay so that time from previous drink would display the last drink time.
addDrink still displays the time of the drink previous to the last drink (second to last drink)

Moved blocks around to make more sense
Created display method minToDisplay for time formatting
Changed calculation

Put features associated with adding a drink (numbers, display, snackbar) into method addDrink
Allowed volume up button to add a drink
Made code prettier

Put display into modules
Changed elapsedTime to prevent null exception
Allowed BAC_calc to return BAC of 0 for no drinks

Changed to Arraylist structure where each drink time is kept track of
Modified some of the logic to accommodate ^
Incorporated UNDO function on snackbar
Changed app name to BAC-track
